nd on the highway. That they operate <img src="/images/article-hreficon-ymmv.png" class="ymmv1 rounded" title="This example contains a YMMV entry. It should be moved to the YMMV tab."><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ValuesDissonance" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ValuesDissonance">without a license</a>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CoolCar" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CoolCar">Cool Car</a>: Rika's Hummer and the prototype buggy.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CoolGuns" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CoolGuns">Cool Guns</a>: Most of them belong to Shizuka's friend, a police officer, and get requisitioned by the protagonists.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Cosplay" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Cosplay">Cosplay</a>: Seen during the <em>"Cosplay of the Dead"</em> subchapter, where Saya, Saeko, and Alice take turns dressing Rei in different fetish costumes<span class="notelabel" onclick="togglenote('note0jqb0');"><sup>note&nbsp;</sup></span><span id="note0jqb0" class="inlinefolder" isnote="true" onclick="togglenote('note0jqb0');" style="cursor:pointer;font-size:smaller;display:none;">see the <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HumiliationConga" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HumiliationConga">Humiliation Conga</a> entry in Rei's section of the character sheet</span>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CrapsackWorld" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CrapsackWorld">Crapsack World</a>: By virtue of a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ZombieApocalypse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ZombieApocalypse">Zombie Apocalypse</a>.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Crossover" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Crossover">Crossover</a>: With <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Manga/TriageX" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Manga/TriageX">Triage X</a></em>, the illustrator's other work, in 