<h2 class="bold font-l">School Girl Betrays Friend</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
High School of the Dead - Ep 01 (Spring of the DEAD): As the zombie outbreak ravages the high school setting. We see two female friends trying to find safety together... least until one of them get grabbed by a zombie coming up the stairs. As she's pulled down she begs for her, but her friend turns out to not be as care as shown before. Thankfully, karma won't let her action slide. </p>
